{
  "stem": "19923.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And because I was short, I was very-- also very fast.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we used to play a game where an opponent would try and hit you with a soccer ball.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And if he could touch you with the soccer ball without you being caught-- without you catching the soccer ball, you'd be out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was able to stand within 3, 4 feet of my opponent who had the soccer ball, and he would take that soccer ball and try and hit me with it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I could duck fast enough to avoid being hit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was that fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I prided myself on my ability to-- to be so fast.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I'm not sure if that ever served me later in life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But in any event, I knew then that I had some-- some ability in sports, and I excelled in sports throughout my life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I remember, though, being a goalie once in the game.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the attacker was coming after me, or coming at me, to-- to score a goal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And just at the right moment, he kicked the ball, and the next thing I knew the lights went out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The lights went out, and I saw stars.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then the next thing I realize is somebody had picked me up and putting me on the shoulder, and he say, you saved the goal with your head.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just in the neighborhood and the school, you know, whatever kindergarten or grade school we had, not organized sports.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, my little sister Regina, in 1930-- she was born in '37.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in 1938, just before we left, she was only 18 months old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So most of my early youth, there were only four of us, and we paired off.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
